{{Quote|But the Saras are weavers and shapers, and they're eager to trade.|Vector Hyllus|<ref name="Star Wars: The Old Republic">''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''</ref>}}
'''Saras''' was the name of the [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive of weavers and shapers. At one point settled on [[Ruu (moon)|Ruu]], the hive and its [[Joiner]]s settled on the planet [[Woteba]] in the [[Utegetu Nebula/Legends|Utegetu Nebula]] after the [[Qoribu Truce]]. The Saras were an artistic colony, building replicas of the [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-Wing]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] flew at the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], as well as the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']], though the [[Gorog|Dark Nest's]] influence had the Saras unconsciously insert tiny Gorog into the replicas.

